# Keep build context small & reproducible. Source is copied explicitly in the
# Dockerfiles; everything below is either regenerated, secret, or host-specific.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.medusa
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.log

# env & secrets — NEVER bake into an image layer
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.template
!**/.env.example

# vcs / ci / local tooling
.git
.github
.husky
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# tests / reports / infra not needed at image build
apps/storefront/e2e
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
infra
docs
.zap
*.md
completion.md
